<HL>
   Action Auto Rental Inc. Shares
</HL>
<DATE>
09/28/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), NO PAGE CITATION
</SO>
<CO>
   AXXN
</CO>
<IN>
INDUSTRIAL &amp; COMMERCIAL SERVICES, LEASING, CLEANING (ICS)
BUYBACKS, REDEMPTIONS, SWAP OFFERS (BBK)
</IN>
<LP>
   CLEVELAND -- Action Auto Rental Inc. said it will buy back
as many as three million of its common shares.
   The auto rental company had about 10.3 million shares
outstanding in August, about 33% of which were owned by
management. The company said share purchases will be made in
the open market or otherwise, subject to the stock's price
and other market conditions.
</LP>
