LODGING, HOTELS, MOTELS, LODGES, CAMPGROUNDS (LOD)
INDUSTRIAL &amp; COMMERCIAL SERVICES, LEASING, CLEANING (ICS)
DIVIDENDS (DIV)
</IN>
