   Elf Aquitaine Plans Stock Split
</HL>
<DATE>
09/28/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B7B
</SO>
<CO>
   EUROP F.AQU
</CO>
<IN>
DIVIDENDS (DIV)
</IN>
